Suryanamaskara A or B

Breath & Movement
Vinyasa means “moving/breathing system”

One technique we can use to deepen this connection is to make the movement follow the breath: begin the movement when you begin the breath. Pace the movement so that it lasts evenly for the duration of the breath.

